data.description: *Open House Saturday 11/25 from 11am to 1pm*ASSUMABLE LOAN at 3% for qualified VA buyers* Stunning views of the Texas hill country offered from this Immaculate Highland Home. Situated at the very top of the Overlook of Stonewall Estates, the spacious interior offers a large open floorplan with vaulted ceilings, large open living space with stone fireplace, dining room, main level office, and a gourmet kitchen with custom cabinets, gas cooking, double ovens and granite countertops. The stunning views can be seen from most areas of the house, including the large north-facing master suite- and the custom outdoor covered patio with built-in grilling area- perfect for entertaining. Upstairs includes a Media room with screen/projector and surround sound for the ultimate movie-viewing experience- as well as a game room currently being used as a billiards area. Custom Private Gym area has been built in below the first floor (walk-out basement style) with easy access from the back yard. Located close to The Rim, La Cantera Shops, and much more. This gorgeous property is ready for a new owner to call it home.
